body:
**This mod is alpha!!!!**



This mod is about exploring the Solar System, fly to planets or battle it out with your friends on many different space ships. Fly high in a space ship and you will be transported to a space dimmension where you can fly to any real life planet you want or build space stations(planed feature).

[ALSO AVAILABLE ON CURSEFORGE](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/the-expanse-a-space-journey)

![Solar System](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5630f1049b93d3b398acf8ea15b6813ea39e4c93_0.webp)

**Right now the mod has:**


-Sun;

-Mercury:

-Venus:

-Earth;

-Mars;

-Jupiter;

-Saturn;

-Uranus;

-Neptune;

-Pluto;

At this point the ships included are:

MCRN Morrigan

MCRN Corvette-class

UNN Truman-class

and some more...
